metadata.name: Under The Veil
metadata.description:
Together, we dance
Under a thin veil
Separating ourselves
From the world.

We dance, forgotten
In our private place
Our safe haven
Under the dying Sun

Away from reality
Our memories undone
Bathed in the orange light
Where we become one

Under The Veil
Photo by Victor Ribeiro 
Painting by Fer Caggiano

Edition: 1/1
Medium: Digital, PNG.
